Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大正时代 有一位以华丽的文体与结构严谨的故事而著称
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誉为天才的年轻作家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字叫芥川龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他年仅23岁时就发表了小说《鼻子》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目漱石读了这篇小说后 在给芥川的信中这样写道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我认为你的小说十分有意思。佩服佩服。”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“你将成为文坛举世无双的作家。”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人菊池宽为表彰芥川的功绩 设立了芥川奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此奖项至今仍是新兴作家的登龙门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那赫赫有名的太宰治 据说也十分崇拜芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位天才的芥川在26岁时发表的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便是这篇《蜘蛛丝》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他所创作的第一篇儿童文学作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大正时期童话作品中也是独树一帜的杰作 享誉极高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（注：明治、大正时期不仅是日本近代文学的黎明时期\N也是儿童文学的变革时期，众多文豪竞相执笔创作了大量优秀的童话）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因名作 更显青涩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:00:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看 《蜘蛛丝》
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是陀多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱 钱你要多少有多少…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然会拿 别吵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊 救命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 都叫你别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少唬弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个谁来送死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妈 我去看庆典
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下 驾到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日是我国恒例的喜庆之日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过百年的漫长岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国能走上如此兴盛繁荣的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在令人庆贺之至 欣悦之极
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:05:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我国仍属小国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后朕将继续与诸位携手并进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团结协助 彼此激励
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待我国更加繁荣富强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请全国人民都拿出爱国之心 忠诚之心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛勤劳作 每日…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有歹人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来者何人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？自然是陀多大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这陀多 太无礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼的是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚咚锵锵的吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放肆 这可是为朕举行的庆典游行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何来无礼之说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下 休要理这种歹人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 铁炮队还没来吗 在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快干掉这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开 挡路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停止这愚蠢的骚动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喊陀多大人万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢人没资格说朕愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢愚弄朕重要的游行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那混账 罪不可恕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪不可恕！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兄弟 请付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陀 陀多…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陀多那家伙 来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吗 叫陀多的大恶棍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 长的就是一张恶人脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我？是吗 你想知道本大爷的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷名叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫长了张恶人脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你善到哪去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还我…还我阿妈来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还我阿妈来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到陀多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜘蛛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不怕我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:11:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子知道我是多有名的恶棍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 跟你说也是白说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然渺小 你也算是条生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便取了你的性命到底是于心不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是和尚的说教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那臭小鬼 搞得我神志不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王陛下 万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是沦为畜生一只的可悲之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字各位早已熟知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是陀多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所犯下的种种恶行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可说是言之不尽 说之不绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是 竟敢威胁朕这一国之王的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必早已有下地狱的觉悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的恩怨可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点下地狱去等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等？那你也会来地狱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了几人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不怕死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说句话求个饶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我问你 活着又算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种世道 活着有什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日复一日年复一年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的生活一直过到死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种生命究竟有什么价值
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这无意义的世界毫无留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丝毫也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还准备了今晚这么盛大的庆典 我真是求之不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣幸之至 还荣幸之去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这邪道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该动手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅样子倒还挺累人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 那就立即让你下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行刑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做 做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人犯 杀人犯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陀多 陀多…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊
